{"id":52335,"date":"2024-02-07T09:32:00","date_gmt":"2024-02-07T04:02:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=52335"},"modified":"2023-12-13T18:29:26","modified_gmt":"2023-12-13T12:59:26","slug":"corner-tv-unit-design-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/corner-tv-unit-design-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"Rejuvenate Your Space With 6 Spell-Binding Corner TV Unit Designs"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Don\u2019t keep cramped spaces empty; maximise space efficiency with corner TV unit designs that leave you spellbound!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>2023 is all about finding a balanced blend of minimalism and modernism. Small apartments and smaller rooms demand the right kind of space utilisation, and corner TV units allow one to be space-savvy and have a beautiful, functional living space. It has become an essential piece of furniture to optimise space &amp; create beautiful decor aesthetics. Our 6 gorgeous corner TV unit designs for small spaces are a class apart! Don\u2019t believe us? Read on and find out.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Wood Corner TV Unit Design With Open Box Shelf Cabinet<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A minimalist corner TV unit can work wonders when you are short on space but high on style. Picture a geometric wall design with a sleek Scandinavian-style TV cabinet that gracefully extends into an open box shelf cabinet. This design offers space for decorative items, books, and more. It is a blend of modern aesthetics and practicality.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13174015\/wood-corner-tv-stand-with-open-box-shelf.jpg\" alt=\"Wooden corner TV stand with open box shelves for easy storage and display\" class=\"wp-image-52342\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13174015\/wood-corner-tv-stand-with-open-box-shelf.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13174015\/wood-corner-tv-stand-with-open-box-shelf-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13174015\/wood-corner-tv-stand-with-open-box-shelf-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13174015\/wood-corner-tv-stand-with-open-box-shelf-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">TV units are the ultimate decor hack<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Modern Corner TV Unit<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>For those who love the warmth of wood in their living space, a wooden slat wall design is a fantastic choice. It showcases your TV beautifully and incorporates a ground-level cabinet with ample storage. You can store your media equipment and books or even display your cherished decor pieces. It&#8217;s a beautiful combination of form and function.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13174005\/modern-corner-tv-unit.jpg\" alt=\"Modern corner TV unit incorporated with a ground-level cabinet for ample storage\" class=\"wp-image-52341\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13174005\/modern-corner-tv-unit.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13174005\/modern-corner-tv-unit-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13174005\/modern-corner-tv-unit-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13174005\/modern-corner-tv-unit-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Ample ground-level storage to your rescue<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Corner Wall TV Stand with Hidden Storage<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Consider a drop-leaf corner TV unit if you have a small living room and need a versatile solution. What&#8217;s unique about this design is the hidden storage behind a flip-up shutter. This innovative feature allows you to tuck away your TV and media equipment when not in use, leaving your living room looking clean and organised.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13173937\/corner-wall-tv-stand-with-hidden-storage.jpg\" alt=\"Corner wall TV stand with hidden storage behind a flip-up shutter\" class=\"wp-image-52338\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13173937\/corner-wall-tv-stand-with-hidden-storage.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13173937\/corner-wall-tv-stand-with-hidden-storage-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13173937\/corner-wall-tv-stand-with-hidden-storage-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13173937\/corner-wall-tv-stand-with-hidden-storage-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">This TV unit is perfect for compact homes<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Floating Corner TV Unit: Wall Mounted &amp; Back Lit<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>For a modern and stylish look, a wall-mounted corner TV unit with floating shelves is an excellent choice. This design typically combines laminate and wood finishes, offering a contemporary feel to your living space. This dual combination finish lets your TV unit seamlessly blend with your existing decor.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13173947\/floating-corner-tv-unit-wall-mounted.jpg\" alt=\"Floating corner TV unit is wall-mounted with backlights\" class=\"wp-image-52339\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13173947\/floating-corner-tv-unit-wall-mounted.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13173947\/floating-corner-tv-unit-wall-mounted-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13173947\/floating-corner-tv-unit-wall-mounted-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13173947\/floating-corner-tv-unit-wall-mounted-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Get more bang for your buck with wall-mounted corner units<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, check out <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/wall-mounted-tv-cabinet-designs\/\">Wall-mounted TV Cabinet Designs<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Low Corner TV Unit with Open Box Storage Shelf<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>While the living room is a common spot for the media station, don&#8217;t forget your bedroom. A decorative corner TV unit can be perfect for your bedroom decor. Keep the bedroom clutter-free with an open box storage shelf while enjoying your favourite shows.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13173956\/low-corner-tv-unit-with-open-box-shelf.jpg\" alt=\"Cosy bedroom features a low-corner TV unit and an attached open-box storage shelf\" class=\"wp-image-52340\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13173956\/low-corner-tv-unit-with-open-box-shelf.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13173956\/low-corner-tv-unit-with-open-box-shelf-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13173956\/low-corner-tv-unit-with-open-box-shelf-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13173956\/low-corner-tv-unit-with-open-box-shelf-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A clutter-free bedroom experience is magical<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Corner TV Unit Design for Living Room: Unique 180-Degree Swivel Feature<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you want the flexibility to watch TV from different areas of your home, consider a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/rotating-tv-stand-ideas\/\">swivel TV unit<\/a>. This innovative piece can turn 180 degrees on either side of the room. Whether you want to watch TV in the dining zone or the living room, the choice is yours. It&#8217;s a space-saving solution that provides freedom and versatility.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13173929\/corner-tv-unit-design-for-living-room.jpg\" alt=\"Swivel TV unit is a versatile corner TV unit designed for living and dining areas\" class=\"wp-image-52337\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13173929\/corner-tv-unit-design-for-living-room.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13173929\/corner-tv-unit-design-for-living-room-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13173929\/corner-tv-unit-design-for-living-room-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13173929\/corner-tv-unit-design-for-living-room-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A flexible screen experience!<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>In conclusion, corner TV units are perfect for those looking to save space without compromising style. From Scandinavian minimalism to swivelling units, there is a unit for every home. Choose the design that suits your preferences and transform your living space into a functional and stylish haven. Consult our team at DesignCafe for more.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>And while you are at it, feel free to check out our frequently asked questions to learn more about corner TV units and make an informed decision.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Explore, More About<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/tv-unit-with-mandir-design-ideas\/\">TV Unit With Mandir Design Ideas<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/tv-wardrobe-designs\/\">Wardrobe Design With TV Unit<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/tv-showcase-designs\/\">TV Showcase Designs<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">FAQs on Corner TV Unit<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1: What are the advantages of corner TV units?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Corner TV units offer several advantages for your home. They maximise space utilisation in rooms. They also provide a stylish way to display your TV and related equipment, enhancing the aesthetics. Additionally, many designs have storage options, helping you keep your room organised and clutter-free.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>2. How to decorate with corner TV units?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Decorating with corner TV units can be an enjoyable process. Choose a design that complements your room&#8217;s decor and style. You can personalise it by adding decorative elements on the shelves surrounding the screen, such as framed artwork, plants, or decorative objects. Make sure your corner TV unit&#8217;s colours and materials harmonise with your room&#8217;s overall colour scheme for a cohesive look.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>3. What sizes are available for corner TV units?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Corner TV units come in various sizes to accommodate various room dimensions and screen sizes. Typical sizes range from compact units suitable for smaller rooms to larger units that can hold big screens. When choosing a size, consider the available space in your room, the TV dimensions, and any additional storage needs.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>4. Are corner TV units suitable for mounting a TV on the wall?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Yes, many corner TV units are designed to be wall-mounted. These are versatile and can save floor space. Wall-mounted units often come with additional features, such as floating shelves, which can provide extra storage space and a sleek, modern look. Be sure to check the product description to confirm if a design is suitable for wall mounting and follow the manufacturer&#8217;s instructions for proper installation.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Functional Interior Designs?<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with smart solutions<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=